---
import ZcalWidget from './ZcalWidget.astro';
---

<section class="how-it-works">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-label">Process</span>
      <h2>From contract to collections in 3 weeks</h2>
      <p>Our proven implementation process gets you results fast</p>
    </div>

    <div class="process-timeline">
      <div class="timeline-line"></div>
      
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Week 1: Integration</h3>
          <p>Connect Kleva to your existing systems. We support all major banking platforms and CRMs. No infrastructure changes required.</p>
          <ul class="step-details">
            <li>API integration setup</li>
            <li>Data migration & mapping</li>
            <li>Security protocols</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Week 2: Training</h3>
          <p>Our AI learns your specific collection strategies, compliance requirements, and customer communication style.</p>
          <ul class="step-details">
            <li>Historical data analysis</li>
            <li>Strategy configuration</li>
            <li>Compliance rules setup</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Week 3: Launch</h3>
          <p>Start with a pilot program, then scale to thousands of calls per day. Monitor performance in real-time.</p>
          <ul class="step-details">
            <li>Pilot program launch</li>
            <li>Team training & handover</li>
            <li>Performance optimization</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="step-number">∞</div>
        <div class="step-content">
          <h3>Ongoing: Optimization</h3>
          <p>Continuous learning and improvement. Monthly performance reviews and strategy adjustments.</p>
          <ul class="step-details">
            <li>Performance monitoring</li>
            <li>AI model updates</li>
            <li>Strategy refinement</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="process-cta">
      <h3>Ready to transform your collections?</h3>
      <p>Join leading financial institutions already using Kleva</p>
      <ZcalWidget mode="popup" buttonText="Start your 3-week implementation" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .how-it-works {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-white) 0%, var(--color-gray-50) 100%);
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .section-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--color-gray-500);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: var(--color-black);
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
  }

  .process-timeline {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto 64px;
  }

  .timeline-line {
    position: absolute;
    left: 30px;
    top: 30px;
    bottom: 30px;
    width: 2px;
    background: var(--color-gray-300);
  }

  .process-step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .step-number {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    background: var(--color-black);
    color: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .step-content {
    flex: 1;
    padding-top: 8px;
  }

  .step-content h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--color-black);
  }

  .step-content p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-gray-700);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .step-details {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .step-details li {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    padding: 4px 0;
    padding-left: 20px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .step-details li::before {
    content: "→";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-gray-400);
  }

  .process-cta {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 48px;
    background: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .process-cta h3 {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--color-black);
  }

  .process-cta p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .timeline-line {
      left: 20px;
    }

    .step-number {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .process-step {
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
    }
  }
</style>